  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Whoa! Wh-What the heck is this!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}Good evening.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}...!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 1 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}Are you surprised?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 1 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 1 25 25}Truth be told, we all visit this world every night.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Wh-What are you saying? Who the hell are you?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 9 0 0}{f 4 23 0 3 0 25 25}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 2 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 2 25 25}Didn't Mommy teach ya any manners? You haven't even introduced yourself.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}C'mon, take a look.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}Name, address, age, etcetera. This is you, right?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Huh!? Where did you get this!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}Somebody's got a grudge against ya, and they asked us to get revenge.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Revenge? What kinda bullshit is this!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Who put you up to this!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}Can't tell ya. We're professionals.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}"Professionals"?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Oh shit... Those rumors online...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}You're sayin' they're true? For real...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}Shall we get this over with now?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Hey... W-Wait... I haven't done anything![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Why me? What'd I do!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}That is not our concern.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}Your notion of right and wrong is irrelevant. My client's wishes are all that matter.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}People hear what they choose to hear, and believe what they want to believe.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}N-No... Stay away...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}{f 5 21 0 4}Get away from me![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 11 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 29 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 11 25 25}You squeal most magnificently![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 11 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 30 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 11 25 25}Such raw emotion![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_018_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 31 0 0}{f 4 23 0 3 0 25 25}He's not dead.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 32 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}Doesn't matter.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 33 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}We held up our end of the bargain.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 212 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 34 0 0}{f 4 23 0 2 0 25 25}Besides, tomorrow this'll just seem like some random crime.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="MSG_020_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 35 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}Well, if there's nothing else...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 211 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 36 0 0}{f 4 23 0 1 0 25 25}I'm feeling rather tired.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
